lead_paragraph: Formula One would be unaffected by any British exit from the European Union, the sport's commercial supremo Bernie Ecclestone said on Monday in an interview in which he supported those seeking to leave.

headline.print_headline: Motor Racing: 'Brexit' Would Not Affect F1, Says Ecclestone
